{"tid":1436250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位去左機場既你我屌哂你地老母","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:53.000Z","uid":102597,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa72faa78ff6a896660c3896d580a2316fcdecc","tid":1436250,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"Sor  標題唔咁樣應該冇人入黎睇 <br />\n<br />\n係咁既 岩岩諗到樣野 鑑於狗隻咁耐以黎既暴行 <br />\n我提議<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣整返份多國語言溫馨提示同狗隻暴行一覽</span></span><br />\n去機場接機既咁多位 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">派俾遊客戈份文宣最上面第一張應該就係張溫馨提示 提醒遊客 小心狗隻 注意自身安全<br />\n下一份就全部都係呢2個月以黎既狗隻暴行</span></span><br />\n再下一份先係成件事既源頭<br />\n<br />\n因為而家黎得香港既遊客應該都對香港發生乜事略有所聞 要知詳細既可以慢慢再了解  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最重要係提醒對方注意人身安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得咁做好唔好<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係睇下大家仲諗唔諗到啲咩去改進/提升返引"},{"pid":"2b1b0918b60d21eb34dc3aad818d43d39979f945","tid":1436250,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54c25326f6d88a11f70836c210d5209cd88a22ce","tid":1436250,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efc08990f3f5fa215904625e04bc7d62fd5a7e38","tid":1436250,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ea6e061f43bf1e935607fd56a4aa5be45ae4e2d","tid":1436250,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06cfa2bdf0ba1ecf3be467d00a8a840b3efa3b75","tid":1436250,"uid":51641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"又標題黨 屌你老母 做乜撚姐你"},{"pid":"3810935b8c69fe0bc9237a624dcec4b52c92407